# Preferred Learning Style
- Start with WHY before HOW
- Visual examples help (use analogies)
- Explain in **Arabic** when concept is confusing
- Use real-world comparisons
- Show me the wrong way first, then the right way
- Tell me common beginner mistakes

# Progress Tracking
Every week, remind me to:
- Review what I learned
- Build something with it
- Teach it back to you (explain in my words)